# Skill: GitHub Commenter

## Propósito

Interagir com GitHub API para comentar em PRs.

## GitHub API Integration

### Autenticação

```javascript
const octokit = new Octokit({
  auth: process.env.GITHUB_TOKEN,
});
```

### Tipos de Comentários

#### 1. Review Comment (inline, em linha específica)

```javascript
await octokit.rest.pulls.createReviewComment({
  owner: "seu-org",
  repo: "seu-repo",
  pull_number: prNumber,
  body: "⚠️ **Security Issue**: Password being logged...",
  commit_id: commitSha,
  path: "src/services/auth.ts",
  line: 23,
  side: "RIGHT", // RIGHT = new code, LEFT = old code
});
```

#### 2. Review (summary geral)

```javascript
await octokit.rest.pulls.createReview({
  owner: "seu-org",
  repo: "seu-repo",
  pull_number: prNumber,
  event: "REQUEST_CHANGES", // ou 'APPROVE' ou 'COMMENT'
  body: `
## Code Review Summary

### ✅ Strengths
- Clean code structure
- Good error handling

### 🔧 Issues Found (3)
See inline comments for details.

### 📋 Action Items
- [ ] Fix security issue (auth.ts:23)
- [ ] Optimize loop (utils.ts:45)

Overall Score: 72/100
  `,
});
```

#### 3. Issue Comment (comentário geral no PR)

```javascript
await octokit.rest.issues.createComment({
  owner: "seu-org",
  repo: "seu-repo",
  issue_number: prNumber,
  body: "🤖 Code Review Agent finished analysis. See review above.",
});
```

## Template de Comentários

### Inline Comment Template

````markdown
{emoji} **{Severity}**: {Title}

{Description}

**Current:**

```{language}
{current_code}
```

**Suggested:**

```{language}
{suggested_code}
```

**Why:** {explanation}

---

_Category:_ {category} | _Severity:_ {severity}
````

### Emojis por Categoria

```javascript
const EMOJI_MAP = {
  security: "🔒",
  performance: "⚡",
  bug: "🐛",
  style: "🎨",
  refactor: "♻️",
  documentation: "📝",
  test: "✅",
  warning: "⚠️",
  info: "ℹ️",
  question: "❓",
};
```

### Severity Tags

```javascript
const SEVERITY_TAGS = {
  critical: "🔴 CRITICAL",
  high: "🟠 HIGH",
  medium: "🟡 MEDIUM",
  low: "🔵 LOW",
  info: "⚪ INFO",
};
```

## Comment Grouping

Agrupar comentários relacionados:

```markdown
### 🔒 Security Issues (2)

1. **Password Exposure** (auth.ts:23) - CRITICAL
   See inline comment

2. **SQL Injection** (db.ts:45) - HIGH
   See inline comment

---

### ⚡ Performance Issues (3)

...
```

## Smart Commenting

### Evitar spam

- Máximo 20 inline comments por review
- Se > 20 issues, agrupar similares
- Priorizar por severity

### Tom construtivo

```markdown
// ❌ Ruim
"This code is terrible"

// ✅ Bom
"Consider refactoring this function for better readability.
Breaking it into smaller functions would make it easier to test and maintain."
```

### Sugestões aplicáveis

Use GitHub's suggestion feature:

````markdown
```suggestion
const sanitized = DOMPurify.sanitize(userInput);
element.innerHTML = sanitized;
```
````

